Fix HUD balance/income + nav by making the HUD self-contained; faster kart

Debug overlay proved the data is correct (coins 1,000,000+, upgrades applying) —
the HUD just wasn't reading it. The cross-script name lookup that updated the
balance/income labels and wired the nav was silently failing.

- HUD.client.lua: now updates its OWN coin/gem/income labels straight from the
  ProfileUpdated remote (with thousands separators), and wires its OWN bottom-nav
  buttons to toggle the panels — no dependency on another script finding it.
  Added a duplicate-HUD guard (StarterGui re-runs this on respawn).
- KartService: bumped speeds (basic 48->75, pro 76->115) and turn rates.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
